# POXY MCU — UI Style

Applies to **Master Control Unit** (`assets/admin-terminal.html`, `/_poxy-staff-mcu`) only.
Consumer app (`index.html`) keeps POXY dark cyber-luxury — do not mix styles.

## Layout (Discord-inspired)

- Fixed **left sidebar** (~220px): logo, theme toggle, nav groups, staff user + disconnect at bottom.
- **Header bar** above content: page title + subtitle (updates per tab).
- **Content pane** scrolls independently; max-width ~1400px, padding 24px.
- Nav item: icon + label, active = amber left border + subtle fill.
- Section title: sentence case; uppercase only for micro-labels (11px).

## Theme (dual light / dark + toggle)

Use CSS variables on `html[data-theme="light"|"dark"]`. Persist in `localStorage` key `poxy-mcu-theme`.
Apply theme before paint via inline `<script>` in `<head>`.

```css
/* Dark (default) */
--adm-bg: #1e1f22;
--adm-surface: #2b2d31;
--adm-surface-2: #313338;
--adm-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
--adm-text: #f2f3f5;
--adm-muted: #949ba4;

/* Light */
--adm-bg: #f2f3f5;
--adm-surface: #ffffff;
--adm-surface-2: #ebedef;
--adm-border: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
--adm-text: #060607;
--adm-muted: #4e5058;

/* Shared */
--adm-accent: #f59e0b;
--adm-accent-hover: #d97706;
--adm-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.12), 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
```

Legacy aliases (`--bg`, `--amber`, etc.) map to `--adm-*` so existing inline styles keep working.

- Theme toggle in sidebar header; **150ms** transitions on `background-color`, `color`, `border-color`, `box-shadow`.
- Tab switch: **150ms** opacity + `translateY(4px)`.

## Typography

- UI: **Plus Jakarta Sans** — never monospace for body chrome.
- Sizes: 13px body, 11px labels, 15–18px section titles; line-height 1.45–1.55.
- **Monospace only** for hashes, UUIDs, serials, ledger codes: `'IBM Plex Mono'`.
- No decorative gradients, glow blobs, or terminal-green UI chrome.

## Cards & tables

- Cards: `border-radius: 8px`, `background: var(--adm-surface)`, `border: 1px solid var(--adm-border)`, `box-shadow: var(--adm-shadow)`.
- Tables: 12px text; sticky header on long views; row hover `background: var(--adm-surface-2)`.

## Status badges

| State | Background | Text |
|-------|------------|------|
| active / ok | `rgba(34,197,94,0.15)` | `#22c55e` |
| pending / warn | `rgba(245,158,11,0.15)` | `#f59e0b` |
| error / blocked | `rgba(239,68,68,0.15)` | `#ef4444` |
| info / neutral | `rgba(99,102,241,0.12)` | `#818cf8` |

## Buttons & forms

- Primary: `background: var(--adm-accent)`, dark text on amber.
- Secondary: border on `var(--adm-border)`; hover → accent.
- Inputs: card surface; focus ring `0 0 0 2px rgba(245,158,11,0.35)`.

## Do / Don't

| ❌ Don't | ✅ Do |
|----------|--------|
| Terminal-green-on-black for whole UI | Neutral Discord-like surfaces + amber accent |
| Monospace everywhere | Sans body + mono hashes only |
| Heavy animations, blur blobs | 150ms transitions, flat cards |
| ALL CAPS paragraphs | Sentence case; caps for badges/labels only |

Preserve existing JS/auth/Supabase logic when restyling MCU modules.
